                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und ein abschrift eins briefs darinn
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> gesant hat, wie die sache und
                        krieg <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durlewchtigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>römisch<ex>em</ex></expan> und zu
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, und dem <expan>hochgeporn<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        fürsten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>herczog<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan> etc., bericht sein, des sein wir
                        fro und hören des <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        künigs, wolgeen in <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, als das wol <expan>billich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        ist. <expan>Sund<ex>er</ex></expan> so <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> für<expan>stenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> wan wir das zu
                            <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>aufneme<ex>n,</ex></expan> und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch,
                        das umb ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt fürbracht, wie daz in von
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan> reten
                        und dienern und in seinen <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> etwievil
                                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und guts
                            <expan>vorzeite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey <expan>worde<ex>n,</ex></expan> des wir
                        und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> unbesorgt warn, als dise
                                <expan>gegenwürtig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>diene<ex>r</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>weis<ex>er</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs,</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> müntlich wol erczeln
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>; bitten wir ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir sie gnediklich dar<pb facs="#facs_168" id="84r"/>inne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und in ewr
                        gnedig <expan>anweisu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> tun wellet, wie sie die sache zu red
                                <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan> und handeln
                            <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> ob in ir hab und gut
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>kert</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möcht, wan wir
                        <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan>, ewr gnade sülle wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen,</expan> daz den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        ungütlich <expan>beschehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ist; und beweiset <add>den
                            unsern</add> ewr gnade und gunst in den <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
                        als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> wol getrawn. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                            <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade allczeit
                                <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>penthecost<ex>en</ex></expan>. </ab>
